</li>
<li>Erika Fairchild Award, Women's Caucus of the Southern Political Science Association (2009)<sup id="cite_ref-profile19_2-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-profile19-2"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>2<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
